OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy and damp start to the
OL,6,Fmorning with light and patchy rain.
OL,7,FBecoming drier through the day with
OL,8,Fsome bright or sunnier spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA fairly cloudy evening and
OL,12,Fnight with occasional mist and fog
OL,13,Fpatches, perhaps the odd spot of light
OL,14,Fdrizzle. Winds will be light and
OL,15,Fvariable.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA mainly cloudy but dry day.
OL,18,FSome mist and fog patches are possible
OL,19,Fin the morning before conditions turn
OL,20,Fdrier and brighter from the south
OL,21,Flater on.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
