OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FLargely dry and settled through this
OL,7,Fperiod with light winds. Plenty of
OL,8,Fsunshine is expected with just a few
OL,9,Fpatches of misty low cloud at times.
